cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper deals with the extraction of topological maps from aerial images, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques. The proposed approach also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) methods to predict objects in a vector representation directly. Finally, the paper also discusses the potential applications of the proposed method in robotics (cs.RO).
